問題，當然是如果債仔冇錢還，金主手上的殼股是否還可以順利出售。為減低法律風險，超級財仔往往都會要求借錢的大股東在證監會作出登記。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/wonder/realtime/article/20180519/58198694\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fwonder%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180519%2F58198694&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSWSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=3d009ff3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fwonder%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180519%2F58198694&h=88d94ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/wonder/realtime/article/20180519/58198694</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:41:34.000Z","msg":"咁風險太高，如果班金主泵水同你打過咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你借得都證明你本身無水，想盡地一鋪，其實咁同賭大細冇咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3bc00e1d484932211b0bb3b93fd951def626d4","tid":1115956,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e4c960ee9acf7bb22da7908bb852b619ef45eae","tid":1115956,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f31a71895b3faa34c1839dcd2023ddc8c0fa1874","tid":1115956,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d4ade385d5979c1f7c6f77ce280d740b6a63903","tid":1115956,"uid":169980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"只可以講，窮人就唔好做莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但偏偏窮莊先會想隻股炒到飛天<br />\n<br />\n街外人參與炒上係真係好普遍正常不過<br />\n咁ga情況未要食貴貨再推，成本係貴左好多者"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:35:30.000Z","msg":"如果已經有外人叉隻腳入黎玩， 正確操作其實係唔係應該趁機沽貨離場？ 起碼小小地都袋左落袋先。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:39:49.000Z","msg":"當你飛現已經太遲，只有搵金主泵水，玩落去，最後咪又係睇邊個錢多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:50:22.000Z","msg":"你講太遲係唔係意思對家已經沽緊貨， 你只好揼錢繼續托個陣？<br />\n<br />\n但係我想講係對家之前應該有個階段係市場買緊貨（如果唔係佢第二日炒起都無貨沽）， 呢個時間如果個莊勤力D做足功課數花既話應該發現有人叉隻腳入黎玩。個時沽貨得唔得？"},{"pid":"981c0c9072b9683839cfa09a39512b94d9e214bd","tid":1115956,"uid":60655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":